data.description: A gorgeous backdrop of White Tank Mountains, sunrise and sunsets from this N/S exposure manicured desert landscaped home on corner lot, leased solar, and modern pool, this single-story stunner has it all. Neutral color palate, beautifully laid staggered tile throughout. Gorgeous wood shutters decorate windows of kitchen, dining and family room. SS appliances, farm sink, and pantry equipped kitchen. Flowing granite countertops and cherrywood cabinets in kitchen, also match bathroom vanities. Rear covered patio, built-in BBQ; wrought iron fence leads to jetted pool, lounge areas, synthetic grass, secure block fence for ultimate privacy. Rare opportunity to seize before it's too late.  Inquire about optional FHA assumable 3.875% rate loan. Estimated processing 60-90 days per lender.
